edu.umd.cs.dmonner.tweater.util
Class NumberRange

java.lang.Object
  edu.umd.cs.dmonner.tweater.util.NumberRange

public class NumberRange
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a range of integers, inclusive on either end. Allows this range to be converted to text and SQL. Capable of extracting ranges from strings such as 13-21 or [8-44].

Author:
dmonner
